verbose_text: To this end, we (1) analyzed the gene expression in A549 cells (human epithelial cell line) treated with 54 chemicals related to diesel emissions by using the DNA microarray method, (2) constructed a prediction model of IL-8 gene expression by using information about the physicochemical characters of these 54 chemicals and IL-8 gene expression and (3) validated the prediction model of IL-8 gene expression according to known data from previous reports.
